<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .order-details {
      background: #fafafa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: block;
      width: 200px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h1>ðŸš— New Engine Order Received! ðŸš€</h1>
    <p>Dear Admin,</p>
    <p>A new order has been placed for an engine. Here are the details:</p>

    <div class="order-details">
      <p><strong>Engine:</strong> <%= @order.engine.title %></p>
      <p><strong>Customer Name:</strong> <%= @order.name %></p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @order.email %></p>
      <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= @order.phone %></p>
      <p><strong>location:</strong> <%= @order.location %></p>
      <p><strong>Quantity:</strong> <%= @order.quantity %></p>
    </div>

